Steps for Logging into EKS via SSO
✅ 1. Enable AWS SSO (IAM Identity Center) and create users/groups.
✅ 2. Create an IAM Role for EKS access and attach necessary policies.
✅ 3. Configure Kubernetes RBAC (Role & RoleBinding) for SSO users.
✅ 4. Edit aws-auth ConfigMap in EKS to map the IAM Role.
✅ 5. Login using AWS SSO CLI:
